There’s not to my knowledge, but you can hide them pretty thoroughly with these two steps:
1. Edit your listing template so the blog authors aren’t linked to.
2. Add this snippet to your template:
```{% if blog_author %}
  {% require_head %}
    &lt;meta name="robots" content="noindex"&gt;
  {% end_require_head %}
{% endif %}```
which will add the noindex tag to the `head` of just your author pages.
